description: The undersea tunnel network cuts journey times between two islands by a half.
title: Faroe Islands: Inside the undersea tunnel network
title_page: Faroe Islands: Inside the undersea tunnel network - BBC News
maintext: The tunnel network will come as a relief to residents, cutting down the travel time between the capital Torshavn and Runavik, from an hour and 14 minutes to just 16 minutes.
